The attempt to create a system to manage the taxonomy for gender is NOT an invitation to manage or limit gender itself.
The goal is to fascilitate clear and nuanced communication regarding gender beyond the capacity of current taxonomies. 
This text is being written on GitHub to encourage colaboration. 

The following is held to be axiomatically true*:
Identity is an aspect of experience which is directly accessable by none other than the thinking being which experiences said identity. 

*Until a better description is found. 
